&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1–3 years managing and moderating online communities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency across major social platforms and their best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong, concise writing with a range of brand voices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort with social analytics and turning data into next steps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proactive, collaborative mindset and calm under quick turns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
