&lt;li&gt;Assist with maintaining recruiting workflows and operational organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help keep recruiting activity moving efficiently across multiple teams and agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support day-to-day recruiting and administrative operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Entry &amp;amp; Systems Organization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
