&lt;li&gt;Help organize talent data within Google Sheets, Greenhouse, and operational trackers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support consistency across documents, workflows, reporting, and candidate pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in cleaning up, organizing, and standardizing recruiting information and processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
